pace-078d1e7f-0856-4120-9db7-97ce5d804833]]\n[[^space-0ff0ae06-293b-402e-bb6c-2fc04cf86f06]]\n[[^space-99b2f524-eb65-4b24-a284-2f6ac8a21441]]\n## Images[[^space-d02b4c97-148b-4e4e-9cc2-e43c0d49a738]]\n[[^space-a37564b0-c1c8-4bf2-82b6-bc7b17586e32]]\n![Minion](https://octodex.github.com/images/minion.png)[[^space-9964cd54-7ebf-4f50-a98b-41ecffb0be61]]\n![Stormtroopocat](https://octodex.github.com/images/stormtroopocat.jpg \"The Stormtroopocat\")[[^space-49d21f13-dc19-4134-80c9-8d2058014762]]\n[[^space-3b8b7d24-a0c4-4d90-91bf-6e9aed94ee2f]]\nLike links, Images also have a footnote style syntax[[^space-ce0a13d6-bbef-46c9-a4e7-c1bb0101da02]]\n[[^space-78f8beda-0caf-4fb5-a6c8-f63ec0afdcf8]]\n![Alt text][id][[^space-fd1a2d5e-8b3c-4b96-b536-bfa44d06f9f7]]\n[[^space-22c2cf16-fbc2-48bf-a77a-a8cc13c553fd]]\nWith a reference later in the document defining the URL location:[[^space-b3dcb7a4-577e-4cb1-b0f6-17da7e0939b5]]\n[[^space-6bb0a14d-7132-4adf-a853-2ecd6360838c]]\n[id]: https://octodex.github.com/images/dojocat.jpg  \"The Dojocat\"[[^space-206c9abe-acd9-4685-8664-372cf64a7497]]\n[[^space-fd5f48dc-f624-49ae-912f-cb80c0d81264]]\n[[^space-1ec2abe6-c1ca-4c67-a23a-25c9c954752b]]\n## Plugins[[^space-f11c4e78-1d41-446c-8b69-eb4dbc026f33]]\n[[^space-54fd52b9-4c9b-46bf-a5a3-51562808c4b3]]\nThe killer feature of `markdown-it` is very effective support of[[^space-56614bd5-3e72-406f-80fa-801ba7714430]]\n[syntax plugins](https://www.npmjs.org/browse/keyword/markdown-it-plugin).[[^space-ac4303cb-8263-48ef-b9c5-26ffc8f74b8b]]\n[[^space-501d9125-b7d7-43f7-97e9-62880611b823]]\n[[^space-49da2a3b-5763-4732-830e-1b4873d5f432]]\n### [Emojies](https://github.com/markdown-it/markdown-it-emoji)[[^space-54508a82-b84c-438e-afdc-31aea0b24811]]\n[[^space-230b0da2-aca9-4886-a2ed-a2296a6fc3bb]]\n> Classic markup: :wink: :crush: :cry: :tear: :laughing: :yum:[[^space-0915feec-954a-4fdd-bf7a-a54f502f6b68]]\n>[[^space-fd6e807e-39cf-4987-8a85-4c91e6eb3061]]\n> Shortcuts (emoticons): :-) :-( 8-) ;)[[^space-1